{"tid":2078560,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(25號活動) 和你論壇 · 初選為左乜","createTime":"2020-06-25T06:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T11:43:35.000Z","uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"03a5d380bca33b4520d8def5f075b4445a2d29b6","tid":2078560,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T06:37:27.000Z","msg":"▉和你論壇 &middot; 初選為左乜<br />\n-<br />\n📍地點：荃灣廣場空地（AEON對面）<br />\n📆時間：2020年6月25日端午節下午5時至7時<br />\n📢主持：荃灣區議員陳劍琴<br />\n🙂講者：民主派初選參選人<br />\n── 張可森 Sam Cheung、 黃子悅 Wong Ji Yuet 、 伍健偉 Ng Kin Wai、 岑敖暉 Lester Shum、朱凱廸<br />\n-<br />\n這幾天落區擺設街站的時候，總會有市民問及什麼是民主派初選，亦有人質疑這是一場「小圈子選舉」。我們幾個民主派初選參選人將在論壇現身說法，解釋初選的重要性以及香港人如何面對國安法危局。<br />\n<br />\n誠邀大家抽空，一人幾分鐘，好好和你論壇。"},{"pid":"8865234064b1169ceeef647f0ba5cf1ea005bcce","tid":2078560,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T06:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4e0b63cf813704dabec8bf01ccb61df8d1ca6f","tid":2078560,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T06:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6829d6531a132b0cdf4ca60599e12121068f33","tid":2078560,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T06:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"776f8569657d4438c835b9b46d165bbe2a1c1535","tid":2078560,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T06:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9672339b3a87ac9ddacb991330e497501cb7b380","tid":2078560,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T06:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527357a1f2c413880c15ed05b2a879e9f775e38d","tid":2078560,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,